The paper discusses the development and application of deep learning approaches in various domains such as image processing, computer vision, speech recognition, natural language processing, and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
